Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兽鬼们 都碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个光辉是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口在愈合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:18.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 那家伙的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总算赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是你做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:27.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:30.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法在寺院里张开防御墙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这道结界只要不从我的意识内消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:38.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就会消除阵内所有伤害我们的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:41.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:44.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会认同的那样的邪术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:52.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这四色之光是幽界深处保护我们疼爱我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:56.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大存在之灵力于现世展露之物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:01:03.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那伟大的存在 就是你们法王厅的圣典内记载的四方的守护天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管表述的语言多么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:09.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳就是太阳 光芒就是光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:11.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使念诵的经文不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:13.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,寻求救赎的心却相同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把差异当成区分和虐待人的原因 是愚蠢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:22.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神的名义是属于神的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人所统辖的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:29.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为何我们的经文中没有这些力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:32.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能像你的咒文那样召唤奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:38.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,寺院是为了使人和天使精灵会面的神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:42.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术师会自己在心中筑造神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要相信眼睛看不到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有怀疑的余地的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:55.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就去看 去感觉 去触摸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:59.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个不得了的小姑娘啊
Comment: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.66,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/------START------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:47.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨龟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨 鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:52.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那种怪物会出现在现世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:13.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,区区巨鬼是无法进入这个结界的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:15.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:24.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个结界对幽体有效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是对物体无效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:28.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:49.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然出现了这种怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不创造机会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,创造施展法术的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 司令员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等 那家伙在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么样也太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,会被踩扁的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不会喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙很适应这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:35.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和我说的一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:44.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经觉得他超乎常人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到已经到如此地步了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:50.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样就干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用魔法只凭自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一个人类能达到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家伙独有的顽强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:08.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和杂兵不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在手臂接好之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是川马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:28.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,川马就是让旅行者在河中溺水的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:31.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不只巨鬼连川马也出现了为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是雨 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是个怪物却会用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,川马是中位灵格的水妖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,同族的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很容易驱使没有自我的低级元素们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雨天的川马是非常危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有视觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它只是顺着自己的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:01.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉罕见的活人的幽体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:02.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:06.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅有兽鬼 连巨鬼和川马也出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是意料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:08.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:09.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拿兽鬼做对手还可以 但
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:16.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是和敌人周旋 争取些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女小姐就趁机念咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:20.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:25.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好保护卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:30.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:31.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跳下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这么短时间内能把风元素活用到如此程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:46.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法解放你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在你旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没想过这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:01.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像我的半身一样的另一个被锁着的灵魂在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,让我被黑暗包围着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:09.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:13.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么至少我要在暴风雨中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不让半身被撕成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:20.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,风之精灵啊 给予我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,无差别摔跤比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个马蟾蜍很适合做我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你随意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:44.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也容易理解这边的家伙 对我的路子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,单枪匹马就把那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快当废物使了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候我什么也办不成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:23.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,德·卡普拉... ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,必须赶紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:28.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,往深处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比这层幽界更深一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个寺院建成之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,位于这个山丘的神殿的幽体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,水之元素
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:08.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的攻击都被水墙阻挡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,与此相比 我却不能防住所有的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到水花会有这样的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被压制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作为魔法初学者 已是无计可施了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:27.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:32.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:34.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高的样子不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:35.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:55.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不止会发射水花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我差点就在地上淹死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多亏这些我也明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,风的力量不止是把东西斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 精灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能斩开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卷起来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:31.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 塞尔彼高那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:54.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 会掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,水从川马身上离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:09.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:20.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么 看见了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是水的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:28.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基现在和水的精灵成为一体了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是被附体啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水的眷属
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,流经此地的谷河的精灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,遵从古老的誓约
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:47.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,清洗污染这片土地的恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我以水底的贵妇人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,向元素灵们发令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把这土地上的邪恶灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用激流冲回冥界的黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:07.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是水本身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集吧 我的眷属们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集吧 聚集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,翻滚 流动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:19.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,地震
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这回又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,河水泛滥 朝这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:42.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快进来 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,会被卷进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:06.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多洛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:23.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兽鬼 怪物们都被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了 我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女大人 魔女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,办到了 多洛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:37.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多洛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基 已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子全部干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多再不醒过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:57.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 和水精同步太强失去自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:58.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:00.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法术解不开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 史尔基小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:10.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在施术的时候被强行唤回会发生什么事...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在史尔基已经去了幽界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:18.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和刚才的水精融为一体 现在一定被困在这流水中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:22.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在心回来之前就唤醒 不知道会对身体产生什么影响
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,稍有不慎 也许会不能回复自我变成废人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底要怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:31.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那个 我记得这个时候要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个杖打拍子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:39.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以一定的节奏打拍子 令施术者的精神集中在现世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,科罗拉这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,节奏是七·七·七拍子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,打三次七拍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:45.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,流动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卷起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用人语表达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,令人焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:59.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和精灵们心灵交融非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:01.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不可被其吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:06.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因此魔法师会在施术是用杖打拍子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来确保自己的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:14.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓魔道 绝不是与力量融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:28.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么 打起精神来 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:50.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:54.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:56.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:24.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那里都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还没找到那两人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能乱动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:38.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急 现在史尔基在寻找两人的气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我沉溺于力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是再做好一些的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:47.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:50.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:55.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这么紧张的话 平时做得到的事也会失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:58.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你拯救了这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人会责备你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:09.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:19.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,两人的气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,两人都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:21.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:24.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 到底要怎样才能做到那么厉害的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:43.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,借助天使和精灵的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救这个村子的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:50.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家教典里的守护东西南北的四大天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有在建起寺院之前 这片土地祭祀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,河流的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,河底的贵妇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:03.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来我曾经听爷爷说过这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:09.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这片山丘以前建有祭祀河神的神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:14.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为长期被遗忘 这次又突然叫出来的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,河流的精灵有些生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因此村子才会被水淹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不成熟的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,房子再建就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:30.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能这样活着 都是靠你的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:32.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我心中对村民的愤怒导致的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:42.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祭司大人 可以的话在这个广场的西边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:46.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能建个祭祀河神的小祠堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:47.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就建吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:50.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,宽容也是神的教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:56.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样的小孩子也能引起那样的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁都可以用魔法的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:02.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使用魔法要花很长时间修行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:07.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是把愿望传达给天使和精灵你们也能办的到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个方法祭司很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:19.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别理我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷子你才是没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:23.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到处乱走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,托那个小个子的福已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先跟你道个谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:33.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,受不起你这个拯救村子的英雄的谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甭抬举我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:37.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:38.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:41.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个四处大吵大闹的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:46.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我有想要给你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:53.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我父亲从海员那里赌赢来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小尺寸小孩子也挥的起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我能收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:02.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一个老人的饯别礼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是逃出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从家计和病重的母亲那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:14.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从所有沉重繁琐的东西中逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想也真是奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:20.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得是勇敢的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但也觉得是天真的逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:27.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的梦想是哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:30.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说你们上年纪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了老头 我那个叫野心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:37.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和天真的梦想等级可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:39.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要证明自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本事是货真价实的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:45.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 东西我就心怀感激的收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:47.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:51.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就行动是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:55.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个寺院的魔法效果还没完全消散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:57.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住上一晚伤口就该好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:00.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有等待的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:03.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,早一刻也好 赶紧出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:11.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:20.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要发呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:21.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.64,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.26,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢我们吧
Comment: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.55,EDChs,,0,0,0,,/--------ED---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:49.23,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}绯红序幕  缓缓拉开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:53.18,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}笑谈之间  揭开舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.11,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}台上一切  皆为戏剧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:00.53,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}循序渐进  如诗如画
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:10.12,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}一字之差  终局俱变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:18.60,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}索然无味  其为传说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:23.92,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}利欲之心  隐于夜中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:27.99,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}日升之前  一触即发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:32.66,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}纯真羽翼  散落人间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.36,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}应着之色  是黑是白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:39.44,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}不得而知  好奇尚异
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:43.32,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}余音袅袅  不绝于耳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:47.24,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}何人愿闻  何人可应
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:52.39,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}虚浮年华  何需再度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:49.23,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}鮮明な赤の緞帳を引く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:53.18,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}歓声の中  舞台へ上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.11,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}全て予定調和の戯曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:00.53,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}狂いは無い  絵画の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:10.12,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}たった一字が欠けた時に結末は変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:18.60,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}呆気無い程に  それが 物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:23.92,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}夜に隠したambition  greed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:27.99,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}朝が来る前に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:32.66,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}無邪気に散り降る羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.36,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}染まるべき色は白か黒か
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:39.44,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}知らない  知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:43.32,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}木霊するostinato
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:47.24,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}誰か聴いて  誰か応えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:52.39,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}仮初の日々はもう要らない
Comment: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.35,OPChs,,0,0,0,,/--------OP---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:25.17,OPChs,,0,0,0,,刻下的烙印如何磨灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:34.63,OPChs,,0,0,0,,任凭他人道长短  殊死之斗又何曾徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:44.97,OPChs,,0,0,0,,暗哑了的嘶吼  依旧在耳畔激荡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:51.22,OPChs,,0,0,0,,笑至尽头之人不是我  亦无怨无悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:55.13,OPChs,,0,0,0,,唯愿能够守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:03:00.77,OPChs,,0,0,0,,诛尽来敌战至终
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.46,OPChs,,0,0,0,,逆天而行破宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:08.40,OPChs,,0,0,0,,思思缠绕神之手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:12.92,OPChs,,0,0,0,,欲断枷锁魂难断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:18.70,OPChs,,0,0,0,,若能终结一切以战止戈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.21,OPChs,,0,0,0,,焚尽我身又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:30.58,OPChs,,0,0,0,,困兽犹斗  逆境之中寻生存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:25.17,OPJap,,0,0,0,,\h\h\h\h\h\h\h刻まれた烙印は  最早消せはしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:34.63,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻くだけ時間の無駄だと  誰が言おうと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:44.97,OPJap,,0,0,0,,また聞こえてくる叫び  声にもならない声で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:51.22,OPJap,,0,0,0,,最後に笑うのはおれじゃなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:55.13,OPJap,,0,0,0,,そこにおまえがいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:03:00.77,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.46,OPJap,,0,0,0,,運命(さだめ)を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:08.40,OPJap,,0,0,0,,断ち切れない  神の手でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:12.92,OPJap,,0,0,0,,結んだ絆と魂を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:18.70,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.21,OPJap,,0,0,0,,すべてを懸けて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:30.58,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻き続けて　生き抜いてみせるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:06.54,Preview,,0,0,0,,腐朽之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:11.13,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}是幽界的黑暗领域 克里科特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.43,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你来殿后 保护女人们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你的灵魂和这样的\N克里科特很相配
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:23.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你在窥视深渊的时候 \N深渊也在窥视你
